summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Public Health Department; amending SMC Section 10.03.010 regarding administrative fees, adding a new section to SMC Chapter 10.03 relating to food-service establishment permit fees; adding a new section to SMC Chapter 10.11 Subchapter XC to provide exemptions from the Food Code, amending SMC Subsection 10.11.911.B to change a code section reference, and repealing SMC Sections 10.11.912 and 10.11.913.
